Class DatabaseRenderer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mapsforge.map.layer.renderer.DatabaseRenderer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RenderCallback

    public class DatabaseRenderer
extends Object
implements RenderCallback
    A DatabaseRenderer renders map tiles by reading from a MapDatabase.
